        'Do not stay in the meditation posture trying to observe the state',
        'Do not close your eyes and try to relax into it',
        'Do not let anyone (teacher, guru, friend) tell you to push through dissociation',
        'Do not practice the same technique again without consulting a trauma-informed clinician'
